'''犹他州同性婚姻'''在经过[[美国犹他联邦地区法院|联邦地区法院]]判决后在2013年12月20日合法化。在法院裁决后，有几十对同性伴侣获得结婚证书。<ref name=tribune2013-12-20>{{cite news |url= http://my.chicagotribune.com/#section/-1/article/p2p-78631026/ |title= Utah County Begins Issuing Marriage Licenses to Same-Sex Couples |first= Jennifer |last= Dobner |agency= [[Reuters|Reuters]] |work= [[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]] |date= 2013-12-20 |accessdate= 2013-12-20 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190527232319/http://my.chicagotribune.com/#section/-1/article/p2p-78631026/ |archive-date= 2019-05-27 |dead-url= yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.sltrib.com/sltrib/news/57292247-78/ruling-marriage-utahns-react.html.csp |title= Utahns React to Friday's Gay Marriage Ruling |first= Jim, II |last= Dalrymple |work= The Salt Lake Tribune |date= 2013-12-20 |accessdate= 2013-12-20 |archive-date= 2016-08-17 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160817022749/http://www.sltrib.com/sltrib/news/57292247-78/ruling-marriage-utahns-react.html.csp |dead-url= no }}</ref>该州总检察长办公室正在对裁决提起上诉。

[[犹他州|犹他州]]是美国第十八个承认同性婚姻的州，也是这些州里政治上最为保守的一州。它是第一个认可同性婚姻而在[[2008年美国总统选举|2008年]]和[[2012年美国总统选举|2012年]]总统大选都投给[[共和党_(美国)|共和党]]的州。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://equalityontrial.com/2013/12/20/federal-judge-declares-utah-sex-marriage-ban-unconstitutional/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=federal-judge-declares-utah-sex-marriage-ban-unconstitutional |title= Federal Judge Declares Utah Same-Sex Marriage Ban Unconstitutional |first= Scottie |last= Thomaston |date= 2013-12-20 |work= Equality on Trial |accessdate= 2013-12-20 |archive-date= 2018-06-12 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180612135740/http://www.equalityontrial.com/2013/12/20/federal-judge-declares-utah-sex-marriage-ban-unconstitutional/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=federal-judge-declares-utah-sex-marriage-ban-unconstitutional |dead-url= no }}</ref>

